Patricia Benoit https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patricia_Benoit 0 Patricia Eloise Benoit (21 February 1927 – 6 August 2018) was an American television and stage actress. She starred as the title character's eventual wife Nancy Remington in the 1950s TV series, Mister Peepers.
